      "id": "PopularPost302765",
      "post_content": "I don't know what people have against this card. Sure, it's a slow Shock with a second effect that doesn't synergize with the first, but as people have been pointing out, it's an excellent pseudo-modal spell. In the early game, you can burn weenies or glass cannons and clear the way for your own attackers. In the late game, it still keeps this utility, since it stops their best blocker for a turn. You'd find a use for it virtually any time you draw it.",
      "posted_by": "Narsus",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost302765\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">I don't know what people have against this card.  Sure, it's a slow Shock with a second effect that doesn't synergize with the first, but as people have been pointing out, it's an excellent pseudo-modal spell.  In the early game, you can burn weenies or glass cannons and clear the way for your own attackers.  In the late game, it still keeps this utility, since it stops their best blocker for a turn.  You'd find a use for it virtually any time you draw it.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '302765'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46763\">Narsus</span>\r\n                                (3/5/2013 7:24:58 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars